    Class Description
    BallotEncrypter  
    ElGamalCrypto
    This class implements an El Gamal encryption key-pair, which can then be used (factory style) to encrypt or decrypt messages.
    ElGamalKeyGenerator
    Used to generate ElGamal public/private key pairs.
    Usage: java crypto.ElGamalKeyGenerator [generator string] [number of keys] [output directory]
